<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹和他的新朋友们在天堂玩得很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们早餐吃了冰淇淋，下午玩儿游戏，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上想熬到几点就熬到几点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天都是假期。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们玩得太开心了，以至于忘记了时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们甚至忘记了自己的家和家人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一次，匹诺曹觉得自己是一个真正的男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他知道自己还是木头做的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以每天晚上，他都会照照镜子，希望看到变化。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天晚上，当他照镜子的时候，他看到了一点变化。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是不是他想要的变化。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的身上长出了毛！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，有人敲门了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“匹诺曹，让我进去！”他的一个朋友喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹不想让任何人看到他的毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在不在。你待会儿再来吧。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“匹诺曹，我知道你在里面，因为你在说话。”男孩儿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在让我进去——快点！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹打开门，门前站着他的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的身上也长出了毛！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“匹诺曹，你必须帮助我！”那个男孩儿喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帮你？我不知道怎么帮你！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看看我，我也长满了毛！”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个男孩儿坐在地上哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，当他们哭的时候，声音听起来像驴而不是男孩儿：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯昂，嗯昂！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，又传来了一阵敲门声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们，你们还好吗？”马车师傅问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马车师傅是他们的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是他把他们带到天堂来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他知道该怎么做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求求你，帮帮我们。”他们喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是声音听起来像“嗯昂，嗯昂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马车师傅看到小男孩儿们后，他的微笑变成了邪恶的笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈哈！现在你们该为贪玩付出代价了。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“几个月以来，你们又吃又玩儿还不工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，你们将变成驴，为我工作一辈子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“驴？”男孩儿们齐声喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是先生。”匹诺曹说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想变成驴，我想变成一个真正的男孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马车师傅听到以后笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个真正的男孩儿？你们只会变成一头真正的驴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他快速地在男孩儿们的脖子上绑上绳子，牵着他们向船走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个被绑的男孩儿想要寻求帮助，但是他们的朋友没有听见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的外表看起来再也不像男孩儿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看起来像驴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要把其中一头卖给农民，另一头卖给马戏团。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马戏团会喜欢一头能说话的驴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹，我想你一定会成为一头出色的马戏团的驴，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为你那么喜欢说话！”那个男人笑着说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把两头驴牵上船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船上有其他看起来很伤心的驴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，匹诺曹知道为什么第一天他看到了那么多驴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和其他的驴开始大哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>